  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "2000-02-16", 
    "text": "Veterans Burial Benefits Improvement Act of 2000 - Increases from $300 to $1,000 the authorized allowance for burial and funeral expenses for deceased veterans who: (1) at the time of death were in receipt of veterans' disability compensation or veterans' pension benefits; or (2) were veterans of any war or were discharged or released from active military service for a service- connected disability and for whom there is no next of kin or sufficient resources to cover funeral and burial costs."
  }, 
